articles.title: Jim Harbaugh won’t comment on Michigan’s legal battle, calls Wolverines ‘America’s team’ - The Athletic
articles.description: Jim Harbaugh said he won't comment on Michigan’s legal battle against the Big Ten until the two sides' hearing Friday.
articles.content: ANN ARBOR, Mich. Jim Harbaugh opened his weekly news conference by saying he didnt intend to comment on Michigans legal battle against the Big Ten until Friday when the two sides are set to present a… [+3794 chars]
